# User Stories â€“ Mobile Application

## User Story 1
As a user, I want to register an account so that I can access the application.

## User Story 2
As a user, I want to log into the application securely.

## User Story 3
As a user, I want to view items on the home screen.

## User Story 4
As a user, I want to view detailed information about an item.

## User Story 5
As a user, I want my data saved locally for future use.

## User Story 6
As a user, I want the app to fetch data from an external API.

## User Story 7
As a user, I want to access application settings.

## User Story 8
As a user, I want to receive notifications from the app.

## User Story 9
As a user, I want to manage my profile or favorites.
